      <description>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Updates from the opening match in the series&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/may/08/england-ashes-dukes-ball-ecb-australia-cricket"&gt;England’s Ashes bowlers lifted as ECB sticks with Dukes ball&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;You can &lt;a href="mailto:nick.miller@theguardian.com"&gt;email Nick here&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/NickMiller79"&gt;tweet him here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p class="block-time published-time"&gt; &lt;time datetime="2019-05-08T14:40:56.847Z"&gt;3.40pm &lt;span class="timezone"&gt;BST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/time&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big sheets are now covering the square at the Oval.&lt;/strong&gt; Might be a slightly longer delay, and we may start losing some time soon. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="block-time published-time"&gt; &lt;time datetime="2019-05-08T14:38:20.845Z"&gt;3.38pm &lt;span class="timezone"&gt;BST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/time&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Eric Loh has a question, regarding the new/old Dukes balls, which are likely to hoop around corners whoever is bowling with them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;“So, I have tickets for the 4th day of the Lord’s Ashes test, should I be worried?”&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2019/may/08/england-v-pakistan-first-odi-live"&gt;Continue reading...&lt;/a&gt;</description>
